7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

snippet.title: Black Friday Shopping Vlog in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video, join me for an exciting Black Friday shopping adventure as I hunt down the best deals and snag some amazing bargains! From electronics to fashion, I’m diving into the biggest shopping event of the year to grab everything on my wishlist. Whether you're shopping for gifts or treating yourself, I'll share tips on how to make the most of your Black Friday experience. It was a very different experience shopping in crowded stores and we were all excited about our lucky coupons. 
#blackfridayshopping #bargainhunting #steffivlogs

This vlog is packed with energy, shopping hacks, and all the excitement that comes with scoring good deals. See you soon in the next vlog adventures!

snippet.title: Gukesh vs Ding Liren | Game 7 | FIDE World Championship 2024 | Ft. Sagar, Tania, Biswa, Balraj
snippet.description:
Watch it LIVE in person in Habitat in Mumbai: https://in.bookmyshow.com/sports/world-chess-championship-broadcast-2024-gukesh-v-ding-liren/ET00420952

The FIDE World Championship 2024 match is the first in 138 years to feature two contestants from Asia, the reigning World Champion, China’s Ding Liren and challenger Dommaraju Gukesh from India competing for the title and a prize fund of US$2.5 million.

The schedule of the World Championship match takes place over 3 weeks, with 14 match days and 4 rest days planned. All games start at 17:00 local time (2.30 p.m. IST) and there are rest days after Games 3, 6, 9 and 12. The first player to reach 7.5 points will be the winner; in the case of a tie after 14 games, tiebreaks will be played the next day to decide the winner.

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

snippet.title: Jetha ने लिए Pav Bhaji & Pani Puri खाखरा के मज़े | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Ke Foodies
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

The breakfast that their wives have prepared for them has left the men of the society feeling let down. The primary victims, Taarak and Jetha, are depressed because one puts uninteresting food on the table and the other postpones breakfast. To learn more, watch the entire episode.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 485
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta #jethalalmemes #tmkocmemes #jethalalcomedy #food #foodies #foodie #gokuldham #fullepisode #comedyvideos #foodlover 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Ke Foodies' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cT5G12J5Crvkt1XPr2dP5iG

snippet.title: ஆளில்லா காட்டிலே | மண்டல விரதம் வீடியோ #5 | Alilla Kattile | Mandala Viratham Ayyappan Video Song
snippet.description:
#ayyappansongs #srihariayyappansongs #symphonyayyappan #srihariayyappa #sabarimalaiselvomvideo  

This Tamil Ayyappan video contains two songs :
1) Alilla Kattile – Album – Mandala Viratham by Srihari
2) Kartigai Matham – Album – Mandala Poojai Ayyappa Sung by Srihari 

Song 1:
00:00 Alilla Kattile
Album: Mandala Viratham
Artist and Singer: Srihari
Music: Srihari
Lyric: Thanu Sundaram Pillai
ஆளில்லா காட்டிலே 
ஆல்பம்: மண்டல விரதம்       
பாடி நடித்தவர்: 'அருளிசை பாடகர்' ஸ்ரீஹரி
இசை: ஸ்ரீஹரி  
பாடல்: தாணு சுந்தரம் பிள்ளை

🌿🙏✨Srihari's Inspiring Mandala Viratham Song: A Pilgrim's Journey to Sabarimala 🌿🙏✨

Experience the devotional spirit in this powerful song from the album Mandala Viratham, sung and performed by Srihari. As the Guruswami, Srihari adorns the Thulasi Mala to the Samimargal (Ayyappa devotees), guiding them on the rituals, fasting procedures, and the challenges of their spiritual journey. The video beautifully captures the pilgrimage in a flashback—from the Irumudi Kattu pooja at their village temple to their trek through the Sabarimala forest, performing the Pettai Thullal at Erumeli, crossing the Azhudha River, climbing the Karimala, reaching the holy Pamba River, and seeking blessings at the Kannimoola Ganapathy Temple. 
 
Song 2:
11:31 Karthigai Matham Malai Aninthu
Album: Mandala Poojai
Artist and Singer: Srihari
Music: Srihari
Lyric: Vijayahari Swamigal
கார்த்திகை மாதம் மாலை அணிந்து
ஆல்பம்: மண்டல பூஜை 
பாடி நடித்தவர்: ஸ்ரீஹரி 
இசை: ஸ்ரீஹரி 
பாடல்: விஜயஹரி ஸ்வாமிகள்

🎶🛕🙏Srihari's Sacred Ritual Song – Araattu Uthsavam 🙏🛕🎶

In this mesmerizing video, Srihari takes on the divine role of a Kerala priest (Melsanthi), leading a traditional procession with the Uthsava Moorthy Ayyappa idol held close in his lap. Accompanied by fellow priests, they journey to the riverside where a series of sacred rituals unfold. 
The video showcases the Sandana Abhishegam, Vibhoothi Abhishegam, and the holy Aaraattu bath, performed with deep devotion for Lord Ayyappa. The priests, along with Srihari, immerse themselves in the river, emerging with wet clothes and blessed hearts, and then return to the temple to continue with further poojas. This song captures the essence of tradition, devotion, and the timeless rituals of Ayyappa worship.

🎧 Listen and Download Now :  
- iTunes : https://music.apple.com/in/album/mandala-viratham/1056538849
- Spotify : https://open.spotify.com/search/Sabarimalai%20Selvoum 
- Jio Saavn : https://www.jiosaavn.com/album/mandala-viratham/Zf,0szRqLlE_
- Youtube : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JU9nNFI-f_4

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Ding vs Gukesh | Game 8 | FIDE World Championship 2024 | Ft. Sagar, Tania,  Balraj, Sahil and Anish
snippet.description:
Watch it LIVE in person in Habitat in Mumbai: https://in.bookmyshow.com/sports/world-chess-championship-broadcast-2024-gukesh-v-ding-liren/ET00420952

The FIDE World Championship 2024 match is the first in 138 years to feature two contestants from Asia, the reigning World Champion, China’s Ding Liren and challenger Dommaraju Gukesh from India competing for the title and a prize fund of US$2.5 million.

The schedule of the World Championship match takes place over 3 weeks, with 14 match days and 4 rest days planned. All games start at 17:00 local time (2.30 p.m. IST) and there are rest days after Games 3, 6, 9 and 12. The first player to reach 7.5 points will be the winner; in the case of a tie after 14 games, tiebreaks will be played the next day to decide the winner.

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | Vahli Gusso Cham Karo Cho | વાલી ગુસ્સો ચમ કરો ચો | New Gujarati Love Song 2024
snippet.description:
Experience pure romance with Rakesh Barot's new love song "Vahli Gusso Cham Karo Cho" only on @SaregamaGujarati 🎶💕

Credits:
Singer: Rakesh Barot
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema
Artist: Rakesh Barot,Neha Suthar
Dop-edit: Chirag Kachiya
Makeup & Hair:  Hasmukh limbachiya
Choreographer:  Deepak turi
Concept: Pranav Jethva, Deepak Turi
Director:  Pranav Jethva
Lyrics: Janak Jesangpura,Jigar Jesangpura
Music: Mayur Nadiya
Creative Head: Dhyey Films & Team
Technical Support: Jenish Talaviya
Rakesh Barot Costume: Manisha R Barot
Spot: Raju,Akshay
Production: Reshma Suthar
Spl. Thanks: Jigar Panchal

Lyrics:
હે હારે મારી ગોંડી હારે મારી વ્હાલી (૨)
એ એ હારે મારી ગોંડી વારે ઘડીયે ગુસ્સો ચમ કરો છો
હારે મારી વ્હાલી વારે ઘડીયે ગુસ્સો ચમ કરો છો (૨)
હારે મારી વ્હાલી વાતે વાતે મોઢું ચઢાઈ ફરો છો
હે કહીયે તારા કીધુ એટલે માથે ચઢી જ્યા
તારા ને તારા મા અમે અડઘા થઇ જ્યા (૨)
હે હારે મારી ગોંડી હારે મારી પાગલ (૩)
આટલો વાનો તમે ચમ કરો છો
હે હારે મારી ગોંડી હારે મારી પાગલ
અમારી વાત તમે ચો માનો છો
હો મારા બુજેંટ ની બહાર ની વાત
ચમ કરી પુરી તમે સમજો  મારી  વાત
હો માળી કોઈ આવક આવતી નથી લાખ મા
ચમ કરી ફરવુ તને ઠઠારા ને ઠાઠ મા
હો તમે શુ સમજો ચેમ હેંડે ઘર નું ગાડું
કરિયાણું લાઈટ બિલ ઘર નુ ભાડું
તમે શુ સમજો ચેમ હેંડે ઘર નું ગાડું (૨)
હે હારે મારી ગોંડી હારે મારી વ્હાલી
એ એ હારે મારી ગોંડી વેત હોય એટલો ખર્ચો કરાય
હે હારે મારી ગોંડી હારે મારી વ્હાલી
નાકમાં વ્યાજ મારા થી ના  ભરાય
હે હારે મારી ગોંડી હારે મારી વ્હાલી
એ એ હારે મારી ગોંડી વારે ઘડીયે ગુસ્સો ચમ કરો છો
મોન્ડ મોન્ડ પુરુ પડે દુજ ના પગાર મા
મજબૂરી જગાડી નાખે  સવાર મા
હો સવાર થી સાંજ નથી જપ પલ વારે
ચી રીતે હેડાડુ એતો મન મારુ જાણે
હે આડીયા તમારા સાઈડ મા મુકો
જઈ કોમ મા માને કરો થોડો ટેકો (૨)
હારે મારી રાની (૨) આભાર તમારો કેવું માની ગયો
હારે મારી રાની તમારા ઉપર જીવ રાજી રાજી થયો (3)

snippet.description:
ఎక్కడో నైరుతి బంగాళాఖాతంలో తమిళనాడుకు దగ్గరలో ఏర్పడింది... పుదుచ్చేరి దగ్గర తీరం దాటింది... కానీ దాని ప్రభావం మాత్రం దాదాపు 1,500 కిలో మీటర్ల దూరంలో ఉన్న ఒడిశాపైనా చూపించింది. ఇదీ...  ఫెయింజల్‌ తుపాను విరుచుకుపడిన తీరు. తుపానుగా మారిన కొద్ది సేపటికే బలహీనపడటం.. మళ్లీ తుపానుగా మారడం.. ఇలా భిన్న రూపాలతో  ఫెయింజల్‌ ఇబ్బంది పెట్టింది. నవంబర్‌ 30వ తేదీ ఉదయం 8 గంటలకు నైరుతి బంగాళాఖాతం నుంచి చెన్నై వైపుగా కదిలింది.
